Im Feld Feedback haben Sie die Möglichkeit, eine eigene Meldung zu definieren, welche dem Absender nach dem Ausfüllen des Formulars im Browser angezeigt wird. Sie können zum Formatieren der Nachricht HTML-Tags verwenden. Wenn das Feld leer bleibt, wird eine Standardmeldung ausgegeben.

<tal:block tal:condition="python:request.get('ZMS_INSERT',None) is None">
<script type="text/javascript">
$ZMI.registerReady(function() {
  $('#BTN_Refresh').click(function() {
    $.ajax({
      type : 'GET',
      url : 'printData',
      data : '',
      dataType : ''
    }).done(function(data) {
        $("#DATA_Preview").html(data);
      });
  });
  $('#BTN_Reset').click(function() {
    var res = confirm("Daten wirklich loeschen?");
    if (res == true) {
      $.ajax({
        type : 'POST',
        url : 'resetData',
        data : '',
        dataType : ''
      }).done(function(data) {
        $("#DATA_Preview").html('0 entries:\n\n\n');
        });
    }
  });
  $('#BTN_Download').click(function() {
    window.open('downloadData');
  });
  $('#BTN_Export').click(function() {
    window.open('downloadData?encode=excel');
  });
  if ($('#sendViaMail').is(':checked') == true) {
    $('#tr_sendViaMailAddress').show();
    $('#tr_sendViaMailFrom').show();
    $('#tr_sendViaMailFrom').next('.zmi-interface').show();
    if ($('#mailFrmt').is(':checked') == true) {
      $('#tr_mailFrmtCSS').show();
    }
    else {
      $('#tr_mailFrmtCSS').hide();
    }
  }
  else {
    $('#tr_sendViaMailAddress').hide();
    $('#tr_sendViaMailFrom').hide();
    $('#tr_sendViaMailFrom').next('.zmi-interface').hide();
    $('#tr_mailFrmt').hide();
    $('#tr_mailFrmtCSS').hide();
  }
  $('#sendViaMail').change(function() {
    $('#tr_sendViaMailAddress').toggle();
    $('#tr_sendViaMailFrom').toggle();
    $('#tr_sendViaMailFrom').next('.zmi-interface').toggle();
     $('#tr_mailFrmt').toggle();
      if ($('#mailFrmt').is(':checked') == true && $('#sendViaMail').is(':checked') == true) {
        $('#tr_mailFrmtCSS').show();
      }
      else {
        $('#tr_mailFrmtCSS').hide();
      }
  });
  $('#mailFrmt').change(function() {
    if ($('#mailFrmt').is(':checked') == true) {
      $('#tr_mailFrmtCSS').show();
    }
    else {
      $('#tr_mailFrmtCSS').hide();
    }
  });
  if ($('#dataStorageDisabled').is(':checked') == false) {
    $('#tr_dataStorageSQL').show();
    $('#dataStorageSQL').prop('checked',true);
  } else {
    $('#tr_dataStorageSQL').hide();
    $('#dataStorageSQL').attr('checked', false);
  }
  $('#dataStorageDisabled').change(function() {
    $('#tr_dataStorageSQL').toggle();
    if ($('#dataStorageDisabled').is(':checked') == true) {
      $('#dataStorageSQL').attr('checked', false);
    } else {
      $('#dataStorageSQL').prop('checked',true);
    }
  });
  $('body #dataStorageSQL').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
  $('body.Manager #dataStorageSQL').removeAttr('disabled');
  $('body.ZMSAdministrator #dataStorageSQL').removeAttr('disabled');
  $('body.ZMSEditor #dataStorageSQL').removeAttr('disabled');
  $('body #BTN_Reset').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
  $('body.Manager #BTN_Reset').removeAttr('disabled');
  $('body.ZMSAdministrator #BTN_Reset').removeAttr('disabled');
  $('body.ZMSEditor #BTN_Reset').removeAttr('disabled');
  var dom = require("ace/lib/dom");
  // add command to all new editor instances
  require("ace/commands/default_commands").commands.push({
    name: "Toggle Fullscreen",
    bindKey: "F10",
    exec: function(editor) {
      var fullScreen = dom.toggleCssClass(document.body, "fullScreen")
      dom.setCssClass(editor.container, "fullScreen", fullScreen)
      editor.setAutoScrollEditorIntoView(!fullScreen)
      editor.resize()
    }
  });
  var edit1 = ace.edit("ACE_Editor1");
  var text1 = $('textarea#optionsJS_'+getZMILang()).hide();    
  edit1.setTheme("ace/theme/chrome");
  edit1.getSession().setMode("ace/mode/javascript");
  edit1.getSession().setValue(text1.val());
  edit1.getSession().on("change",function() {
    text1.val(edit1.getSession().getValue()).change();
  });
  var edit2 = ace.edit("ACE_Editor2");
  var text2 = $('textarea#onReadyJS_'+getZMILang()).hide();
  edit2.setTheme("ace/theme/chrome");
  edit2.getSession().setMode("ace/mode/javascript");    
  edit2.getSession().setValue(text2.val());
  edit2.getSession().on("change",function() {
    text2.val(edit2.getSession().getValue()).change();
  });
  var edit3 = ace.edit("ACE_Editor3");
  var text3 = $('textarea#onChangeJS_'+getZMILang()).hide();
  edit3.setTheme("ace/theme/chrome");
  edit3.getSession().setMode("ace/mode/javascript");    
  edit3.getSession().setValue(text3.val());
  edit3.getSession().on("change",function() {
    text3.val(edit3.getSession().getValue()).change();
  });
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$ZMI.registerReady(function() {
  $('#tabProperties .accordion-inner').attr('class','accordion-inner ' + $('#tr_type_'+getZMILang()+' :selected').text());
  $('#tr_replyToField_'+getZMILang()).hide();
  $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).hide();
  $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).next('.zmi-interface').hide();
  $('#tr_type_'+getZMILang()+' select').change(function() {
    $('#tabProperties .accordion-inner').attr('class','accordion-inner ' + $('#tr_type_'+getZMILang()+' :selected').text());
    if ($('#tr_type_'+getZMILang()+' select').val() != 'custom') {
      $('#ACE_Editor1').hide();
      $('.ACE_Editor').height(0);
    }
    else {
      $('#ACE_Editor1').show();
      $('.ACE_Editor').height('20em');
    }
    if ($('#tr_type_'+getZMILang()+' select').val() == 'email') {
      $('#tr_replyToField_'+getZMILang()).show();
      $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).show();
      $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).next('.zmi-interface').show();
    }
    else {
      $('#tr_replyToField_'+getZMILang()).hide();
      $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).hide();
      $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).next('.zmi-interface').hide();
    }
  });
  if ($('#tr_type_'+getZMILang()+' select').val() != 'custom') {
    $('#ACE_Editor1').hide();
  }
  if ($('#tr_type_'+getZMILang()+' select').val() == 'email') {
    $('#tr_replyToField_'+getZMILang()).show();
    $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).show();
    $('#tr_copyToField_'+getZMILang()).next('.zmi-interface').show();
  }
  var dom = require("ace/lib/dom");
  // add command to all new editor instances
  require("ace/commands/default_commands").commands.push({
    name: "Toggle Fullscreen",
    bindKey: "F10",
    exec: function(editor) {
      var fullScreen = dom.toggleCssClass(document.body, "fullScreen")
      dom.setCssClass(editor.container, "fullScreen", fullScreen)
      editor.setAutoScrollEditorIntoView(!fullScreen)
      editor.resize()
    }
  });
  var edit1 = ace.edit("ACE_Editor1");
  var text1 = $('textarea#rawJSON_'+getZMILang()).hide(); 
  edit1.setTheme("ace/theme/chrome");
  edit1.getSession().setMode("ace/mode/javascript");
  edit1.getSession().setValue(text1.val());
  edit1.getSession().on("change",function() {
  text1.val(edit1.getSession().getValue()).change();
  });
});
</script>

from zms3.formulator import ZMSFormulator import zExceptions
def printData(self): current_roles = self.getUserRoles(self.REQUEST['AUTHENTICATED_USER']) allowed_roles = ['Manager','ZMSAdministrator','ZMSEditor'] authorized = len(self.intersection_list(current_roles,allowed_roles))>0 and True or False if not authorized: raise zExceptions.Unauthorized else: frmu = ZMSFormulator.ZMSFormulator(self) self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Cache-Control', 'no-cache') self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Pragma', 'no-cache') self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Content-Type','text/html; charset=utf-8') data = frmu.printDataRaw() data = unicode(data,'utf-8') return data.replace('#/#',' | ')

from zms3.formulator import ZMSFormulator
def putData(self):
# Workaround: adding language for forms existing only in a secondary language self.REQUEST.set('lang',self.REQUEST.form.get('LANG', self.getPrimaryLanguage()))
frmu = ZMSFormulator.ZMSFormulator(self) res = frmu.receiveData() self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Cache-Control', 'no-cache') self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Pragma', 'no-cache') self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Content-Type','text/html; charset=utf-8') if res: return 'OK' else: return 'NOK'

from zms3.formulator import ZMSFormulator import zExceptions import HTMLParser
def downloadData(self): current_roles = self.getUserRoles(self.REQUEST['AUTHENTICATED_USER']) allowed_roles = ['Manager','ZMSAdministrator','ZMSEditor'] authorized = len(self.intersection_list(current_roles,allowed_roles))>0 and True or False if not authorized: raise zExceptions.Unauthorized else: frmu = ZMSFormulator.ZMSFormulator(self) html = HTMLParser.HTMLParser() content_type = 'text/csv; charset=utf-8' filename = '"%s_%s_%s.csv"'%(self.getLangStr('TYPE_ZMSFORMULATOR'),frmu.titlealt,frmu.this.getId()) self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Content-Type',content_type) self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Content-Disposition','attachment;filename='+filename) self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Cache-Control', 'no-cache') self.REQUEST.RESPONSE.setHeader('Pragma', 'no-cache') data = frmu.printDataRaw(frmt='csv') if (self.REQUEST.get('encode','')=='excel'): data = html.unescape(unicode(data,'utf-8')).encode('latin-1',errors='xmlcharrefreplace') tab = {'ä':228,'ö':246,'ü':252,'Ö':214,'Ä':196,'Ü':220,'é':233,'è':232, 'ê':234,'à':224,'â':226,'ò':242,'ô':244,'ù':249,'û':251} for t in tab: if data.find(t) >= 0: data = data.replace(t, chr(tab[t])) # preserve variants of apostrophes data = data.replace(''','\'') data = data.replace('ʻ','\'') data = data.replace('ʼ','\'') data = data.replace('ˮ','\'') data = data.replace('՚','\'') data = data.replace('‘','\'') data = data.replace('’','\'') data = data.replace('‚','\'') data = data.replace('‛','\'') data = data.replace('‹','\'') data = data.replace('›','\'') data = data.replace('Ꞌ','\'') data = data.replace('ꞌ','\'') data = data.replace('＇','\'') # preserve variants of quotation marks data = data.replace('"','"') data = data.replace('«','"') data = data.replace('»','"') data = data.replace('“','"') data = data.replace('”','"') data = data.replace('„','"') data = data.replace('‟','"') data = data.replace('〝','"') data = data.replace('〞','"') data = data.replace('〟','"') data = data.replace('＂','"') else: data = html.unescape(unicode(data,'utf-8')) return data
